title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Soaps, Organic Agents, Lubricants, Waxes
description: Imports Intra Eu - Soaps, Organic Agents, Lubricants, Waxes in the United Kingdom decreased to 155.10 GBP Million in September from 197.43 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Soaps, Organic Agents, Lubrican in the United Kingdom averaged 85.64 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 197.43 GBP Million in August of 2022 and a record low of 28.96 GBP Million in December of 1996.
